---
title: Creamy Curried Cauliflower Soup with Roasted Chickpeas and Cheese
description: Our Creamy Curried Cauliflower Soup is a delicious veggie option that makes it easy to eat more veg in your diet and try something new!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R20_W33_UK_V13414-3_Main_3_low-90ef1ae4.jpg
